<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 16:07:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列阿拉伯社区的谋杀率自战争开始以来下降后大幅上升</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/murder-rate-in-israels-arab-communities-surges-after-plunging-since-start-of-war/0000018c-7853-d55c-a7cc-fb5793470000</link><description>哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列后，阿拉伯社区的凶杀率与战前六个月相比减少了一半，但现在已恢复到之前的水平。警方将这一上升归因于该国大部分地区恢复了相对正常的生活状态，以及现场警力的减少</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 15:53:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/murder-rate-in-israels-arab-communities-surges-after-plunging-since-start-of-war/0000018c-7853-d55c-a7cc-fb5793470000</guid></item><item><title>第三季度 GDP 下调、通胀放缓后以色列可能降息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-rate-cuts-possible-after-q3-gdp-revised-down-inflation-eases/0000018c-7832-d301-a3ac-fef3d4460000</link><description>2023年以色列经济增长放缓，部分原因是战争的负面影响。明年的增长很大程度上取决于战争的持续时间以及冲突是否仍然局限于加沙或蔓延到其他战线</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 15:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-rate-cuts-possible-after-q3-gdp-revised-down-inflation-eases/0000018c-7832-d301-a3ac-fef3d4460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙发现迄今为止最大的哈马斯隧道系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-uncovers-large-hamas-tunnel-found-so-far-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-7841-d301-a3ac-fec1da5a0000</link><description>军方称，这条隧道长四公里，宽三米，是为了车辆通过而设计的</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 15:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-uncovers-large-hamas-tunnel-found-so-far-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-7841-d301-a3ac-fec1da5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名了周六在加沙战斗中丧生的两名预备役士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israeli-army-names-two-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-saturday/0000018c-7816-d55c-a7cc-fb16167b0000</link><description>自以色列国防军在加沙地带开始地面行动以来，已有121名以色列士兵在哈马斯统治的加沙地带内丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 14:59:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israeli-army-names-two-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-saturday/0000018c-7816-d55c-a7cc-fb16167b0000</guid></item><item><title>不仅仅是大学校园：以色列-加沙战争的紧张局势蔓延到美国公立学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-just-college-campuses-tensions-from-israel-gaza-war-spill-into-u-s-public-schools/0000018c-7733-df88-a39c-77b395160000</link><description>自10月7日以来，美国中小学反犹太事件明显增多，学生和家长对反犹太主义和反以色列对抗的加剧以及孩子们所接受的教育感到担忧</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 14:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-just-college-campuses-tensions-from-israel-gaza-war-spill-into-u-s-public-schools/0000018c-7733-df88-a39c-77b395160000</guid></item><item><title>去世前几小时，他在加沙一所学校的黑板上画下了最后的艺术作品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-drew-his-last-sketch-on-a-gaza-school-blackboard-hours-before-he-died/0000018c-691b-db38-a9fc-e9bb694b0000</link><description>尤纳坦·哈佐尔 (Yonatan Hatzor) 是一支精英部队的成员。他的创作具有人性，但他所描绘的恐怖却预示着他的死亡。 “他是我认识的最强壮的人，但他画得很精致。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 14:32:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-drew-his-last-sketch-on-a-gaza-school-blackboard-hours-before-he-died/0000018c-691b-db38-a9fc-e9bb694b0000</guid></item><item><title>这位加沙诗人在以色列空袭中丧生，突破封锁边界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/killed-in-an-israeli-airstrike-this-gaza-poet-broke-through-a-blockades-borders/0000018c-77ee-d1e1-a3ae-77eee0560000</link><description>雷法特·阿拉雷尔 (Refaat Alareer) 与几位亲密的家人一起去世，他用英语写下了加沙的生活。作为以色列的严厉批评者，他教导年轻的加沙人利用他们的写作作为巴勒斯坦抵抗的工具</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 14:04:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/killed-in-an-israeli-airstrike-this-gaza-poet-broke-through-a-blockades-borders/0000018c-77ee-d1e1-a3ae-77eee0560000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列公民和居民在战争期间在雷达之下离开加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-citizens-and-residents-left-gaza-during-the-war-under-the-radar/0000018c-77e6-de9c-aded-7fee8d700000</link><description>过去一个月，71 名妇女、男子和儿童步行、乘坐以燃气为燃料的汽车和特殊班车离开加沙地带前往以色列。他们向《国土报》讲述了自己的经历以及对那些留下来的人的担忧</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 13:41:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-citizens-and-residents-left-gaza-during-the-war-under-the-radar/0000018c-77e6-de9c-aded-7fee8d700000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙战争对以色列人来说最悲惨的时刻之一，内塔尼亚胡逃避责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/at-one-of-the-wars-most-tragic-moments-for-israelis-netanyahu-shirks-from-responsibility/0000018c-77b8-d250-a1af-ffbf782b0000</link><description>人质获释后，以色列总理欣喜若狂，但派军方发言人宣布人质死亡。内塔尼亚胡的办公室也无视人质家庭论坛的会议要求，而拜登则为美国和以色列人质家庭腾出了两个小时的时间</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 13:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/at-one-of-the-wars-most-tragic-moments-for-israelis-netanyahu-shirks-from-responsibility/0000018c-77b8-d250-a1af-ffbf782b0000</guid></item><item><title>报道哈马斯针对以色列妇女的非人性性暴力行为的伦理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/the-ethics-of-covering-hamas-dehumanizing-sexual-violence-against-israeli-women/0000018c-5e45-d798-adac-feef6cb80000</link><description>以色列应该小心，不要让其对打击针对妇女的性暴力的国际组织可耻的无动于衷的愤怒，不要演变成对哈马斯战争罪行受害者的人性和隐私的难以承受的打击。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 12:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/the-ethics-of-covering-hamas-dehumanizing-sexual-violence-against-israeli-women/0000018c-5e45-d798-adac-feef6cb80000</guid></item><item><title>释放我儿子的巴勒斯坦杀手，以释放哈马斯扣押的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/free-my-sons-palestinian-killer-to-free-the-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018c-76ce-db38-a9fc-ffee21580000</link><description>只要婴儿、父亲、母亲和兄弟仍被困在加沙，整个以色列都是哈马斯的人质，人质家庭的处境最为严重。这就是为什么我呼吁释放杀害我心爱儿子的狙击手，如果这能带回他们的亲人之一</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:43:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/free-my-sons-palestinian-killer-to-free-the-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018c-76ce-db38-a9fc-ffee21580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列枪支许可机构负责人表示，本格维尔的政策导致“失控”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/head-of-israels-gun-licensing-authority-ben-gvirs-policy-leading-to-loss-of-control/0000018c-767f-db38-a9fc-fffffa160000</link><description>负责批准枪支许可证的以色列官员敦促极右翼部长改变其政策，因为有消息称本-格维尔的同伙已被任命在未经必要授权的情况下处理请求</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:14:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/head-of-israels-gun-licensing-authority-ben-gvirs-policy-leading-to-loss-of-control/0000018c-767f-db38-a9fc-fffffa160000</guid></item><item><title>五名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸丧生，四人死于以色列军队无人机袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-four-from-israeli-army-drone-strike/0000018c-7731-dabb-afae-77b355360000</link><description>这次袭击是在巴勒斯坦城市图尔卡尔姆连夜进行的，是以色列国防军自战争开始以来在该地区第二次“制止恐怖”行动之际进行的</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-four-from-israeli-army-drone-strike/0000018c-7731-dabb-afae-77b355360000</guid></item><item><title>法国外交部称工人在以色列对加沙拉法的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/french-foreign-ministry-says-worker-killed-by-an-israeli-strike-in-gazas-rafah/0000018c-7724-dbd5-a39c-ff772e860000</link><description>法国外交部表示：“我们要求以色列当局尽快全面了解这起爆炸事件的情况。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 09:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/french-foreign-ministry-says-worker-killed-by-an-israeli-strike-in-gazas-rafah/0000018c-7724-dbd5-a39c-ff772e860000</guid></item><item><title>半岛电视台将以色列袭击导致加沙摄影师死亡案件移交国际刑事法院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/al-jazeera-to-refer-death-of-cameraman-in-gaza-from-israeli-strike-to-icc/0000018c-76e1-dbd5-a39c-fff376d80000</link><description>据半岛电视台报道，摄影师萨米尔·阿布·达卡 (Samer Abu Daqqa) 在报道早些时候对加沙学校的爆炸事件时，在以色列无人机袭击中身亡。以色列国防军表示“从未”故意针对记者</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 09:24:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/al-jazeera-to-refer-death-of-cameraman-in-gaza-from-israeli-strike-to-icc/0000018c-76e1-dbd5-a39c-fff376d80000</guid></item><item><title>报告：摩萨德负责人与卡塔尔总理就人质协议进行“积极”会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-live/idf-names-two-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat-palestinians-two-killed-in-w-bank/0000018c-75f4-db38-a9fc-fdf659620000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵的名字 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称，五人在西岸图尔卡姆附近的以色列无人机袭击中丧生 ■ 美国国防部长启程前往以色列 ■ 来自黎巴嫩的反坦克导弹击中以色列北部基布兹的建筑物 ■ 至少 1,200 名平民和自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列有士兵被杀；加沙至少 130 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 18,608 人死亡，50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 04:31:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-live/idf-names-two-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat-palestinians-two-killed-in-w-bank/0000018c-75f4-db38-a9fc-fdf659620000</guid></item><item><title>据《纽约时报》报道，以色列在发现哈马斯价值 5 亿美元的资产后没有采取行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-failed-to-act-after-finding-hamas-assets-worth-half-a-billion-dollars-nyt-reports/0000018c-74e3-d48b-a5ec-74f382e00000</link><description>自 2018 年以来，以色列和美国高级官员都知道详细介绍哈马斯网络的秘密文件，价值数亿美元，目前据信这些文件为 10 月 7 日的袭击提供了资金</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 02:44:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-failed-to-act-after-finding-hamas-assets-worth-half-a-billion-dollars-nyt-reports/0000018c-74e3-d48b-a5ec-74f382e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质在雷伊姆附近的聚会中被绑架，在囚禁期间被哈马斯谋杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-kidnapped-from-party-near-reim-murdered-by-hamas-while-in-captivity/0000018c-749a-d48b-a5ec-74dbea7f0000</link><description>27 岁的因巴尔·海曼 (Inbar Haiman) 成功躲避哈马斯恐怖分子两个小时，然后于 10 月 7 日被拖到加沙。她是一名涂鸦艺术家，正在学习视觉传达</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 01:55:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-kidnapped-from-party-near-reim-murdered-by-hamas-while-in-captivity/0000018c-749a-d48b-a5ec-74dbea7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部贝都因小镇男子被枪杀，警方正在调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-to-death-in-southern-israeli-bedouin-town-police-investigating/0000018c-7541-dbd5-a39c-ff7371ad0000</link><description>以色列警方怀疑这名 29 岁的男子因家庭不和而被枪杀。这起谋杀案是本周末发生的第三起疑似谋杀案</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 01:38:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-to-death-in-southern-israeli-bedouin-town-police-investigating/0000018c-7541-dbd5-a39c-ff7371ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方逮捕两人并驱散以色列北部的反加沙战争抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-two-disperse-anti-gaza-war-protest-in-northern-israel/0000018c-7496-d48b-a5ec-74d7d0d70000</link><description>参加示威的人数不到20人，但现场有很多警察。一名被拘留的抗议者说，我们站在那里进行合法的抗议守夜活动，没有打扰任何人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 00:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-two-disperse-anti-gaza-war-protest-in-northern-israel/0000018c-7496-d48b-a5ec-74d7d0d70000</guid></item></channel></rss>